quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  48,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  48,1,( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) hum ne tum ko fatah di. fatah bhi Sarih وصاف
  48,2,taakay khuda tumahray aglay aur pichlle gunah bakhash day aur tum par apni Nemat poori kardey aur tumhe seedhay raste chalaye
  48,3,aur khuda tumhari zabardast madad kere
  48,4,wohi to hai jis ne mominoun ke dilon par tasalii nazil farmai taakay un ke imaan ke sath aur imaan barhay. aur asmano aur zameen ke lashkar ( sab ) khuda hi ke hain. aur khuda jan-nay wala ( aur ) hikmat wala hai
  48,5,( yeh ) is liye ke woh momin mardon aur momin aurton ko bahishtoon mein jin ke neechay nehrain beh rahi hain daakhil kere woh is mein hamesha rahen ge aur un se un ke gunaaho ko daur kardey. aur yeh khuda ke nazdeek barri kamyabi hai
  48,6,aur ( is liye ke ) munhafiq mardon aur munhafiq aurton aur mushriq mardon aur mushriq aurton ko jo khuda ke haq mein buray buray khayaal rakhtay hain azaab day. un hi par buray haadsay waqay hon. aur khuda un par ghusse howa aur un par laanat ki aur un ke liye dozakh tayyar ki. aur woh buri jagah hai
  48,7,aur asmano aur zameen ke lashkar khuda hi ke hain. aur khuda ghalib ( aur ) hikmat wala hai
  48,8,aur hum ne ( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) tum ko haq zahir karne wala aur khushkhabri sunanay wala aur khauf dilanay wala ( bana kar ) bheja hai
  48,9,taakay ( mslmano ) tum log khuda par aur is ke paighambar par imaan lao aur is ki madad karo aur is ko buzurag samjhoo. aur subah vsham is ki tasbeeh karte raho
  48,10,jo log tum se baet karte hain woh khuda se baet karte hain. khuda ka haath un ke hathon par hai. phir jo ehad ko torrey to ehad tornay ka nuqsaan isi ko hai. aur jo is baat ko jis ka is ne khuda se ehadkiya hai poora kere to woh usay anqareeb ajar azeem day ga
  48,11,jo ganwar peechay reh gay woh tum se kahin ge ke hum ko hamaray maal aur ahal vayal ne rok rakha aap hamaray liye ( khuda se ) bakhshish mangeen. yeh log apni zabaan se woh baat kehte hain jo un ke dil mein nahi hai. keh do ke agar khuda tum ( logon ) ko nuqsaan pahunchana chahay ya tumhe faida pohanchanay ka iradah farmaiye to kon hai jo is ke samnay tumahray liye kisi baat ka kuch ikhtiyar rakhay ( koi nahi ) balkay jo kuch tum karte ho khuda is se waaqif hai
  48,12,baat yeh hai ke tum log yeh samajh baithy they ke paighambar aur momin apne ahal vayal mein kabhi lout kar anay hi ke nahi. aur yahi baat tumahray dilon ko achi maloom hui. aur ( isi wajah se ) tum ne buray buray khayaal kiye aur ( aakhir kaar ) tum halakat mein par gay
  48,13,aur jo shakhs khuda par aur is ke paighambar par imaan nah laaye to hum ne ( aisay ) kafiroon ke liye aag tayyar kar rakhi hai
  48,14,aur asmano aur zameen ki badshahi khuda hi ki hai. woh jisay chahay bakhshay aur jisay chahay saza day. aur khuda bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  48,15,jab tum log ghanimatainlainay chalo ge to jo log peechay reh gay they woh kahin ge hamein bhi ijazat dijiye ke aap ke sath chalein. yeh chahtay hain ke khuda ke qoul ko badal den. keh do ke tum hargiz hamaray sath nahi chal satke. isi terhan khuda ne pehlay se farma diya hai. phir kahin ge ( nahi ) tum to hum se hasad karte ho. baat yeh hai ke yeh log samajte hi nahi magar bohat kam
  48,16,jo ganwar peechay reh gay they un se keh do ke tum aik sakht jangju qoum ke ( sath larai ke ) liye bulaye jao ge un se tum ( ya to ) jung karte raho ge ya woh islam le ayen ge. agar tum hukum manu ge to khuda tum ko acha badla day ga. aur agar munh phair lau ge jaisay pehli dafaa phera tha to woh tum ko buri takleef ki saza day ga
  48,17,nah to andhay par gunah hai ( ke safar jung se peechay reh jaye ) aur nah lngrhe par gunah hai aur nah bemaar par gunah hai. aur jo shakhs khuda aur is ke paighambar ke farmaan par chalay ga khuda is ko bahishtoon mein daakhil kere ga jin ke taley nehrain beh rahi hain. aur jo rogrdani kere ga usay buray dukh ki saza day ga
  48,18,( ae paighambar ) jab momin tum se darakht ke neechay baet kar rahay they to khuda un se khush howa. aur jo ( Sadaq o khaloos ) un ke dilon mein tha woh is ne maloom karliya. to un par tasalii nazil farmai aur inhen jald fatah inayat ki
  48,19,aur bohat si ghanimatainjo unhon ne haasil kee. aur khuda ghalib hikmat wala hai
  48,20,khuda ne tum se bohat si ghanimaton ka wada farmaya ke tum un ko haasil karo ge so is ne ghanemat ki tumahray liye jaldi farmai aur logon ke haath tum se rok diye. gharz yeh thi ke yeh mominoun ke liye ( khuda ki ) qudrat ka namona ho aur woh tum ko seedhay raste par chalaye
  48,21,aur aur ( ghanimatainden ) jin par tum qudrat nahi rakhtay they ( aur ) woh khuda hi ki qudrat mein theen. aur khuda har cheez par Qadir hai
  48,22,aur agar tum se kafir lartay to peeth phair kar bhaag jatay phir kisi ko dost nah paate aur nah madadgaar
  48,23,( yahi ) khuda ki aadat hai jo pehlay se chali aati hai. aur tum khuda ki aadat kabhi badalti nah dekho ge
  48,24,aur wohi to hai jis ne tum ko un ( kafiroon ) par fatahyaab karne ke baad sarhad mecca mein un ke haath tum se aur tumahray haath un se rok diye. aur jo kuch tum karte ho khuda is ko dekh raha hai
  48,25,yeh wohi log hain jinhon ne kufarkiya aur tum ko masjid haraam se rok diya aur qurbanion ko bhi ke apni jagah pounchanay se ruki rahen. aur agar aisay musalman mard aur musalman aurtain nah hoten jin ko tum jantay nah they ke agar tum un ko pamaal kar dete to tum ko un ki taraf se be khaberi mein nuqsaan poanch jata. ( to bhi tumahray haath se fatah hojati magar takheer ) is liye ( hui ) ke khuda apni rehmat mein jis ko chahay daakhil karle. aur agar dono fareeq allag allag ho jatay to jo un mein kafir they un hum dukh dainay wala azaab dete
  48,26,jab kafiroon ne apne dilon mein zid ki aur zid bhi jahliat ki. to khuda ne apne paighambar aur mominoun par apni taraf se taskeen nazil farmai aur un ko parhaiz gari ki baat par qaim rakha aur woh isi ke mustahiq aur ahal they. aur khuda har cheez se khabardaar hai
  48,27,be shak khuda ne apne paighambar ko sacha ( aur ) sahih khawab dekhaya. ke tum khuda ne chaha to masjid haraam mein apne sir mndwa kar aur apne baal کتروا kar aman o aman se daakhil hogay. aur kisi terhan ka khauf nah karo ge. jo baat tum nahi jantay they is ko maloom thi so is ne is se pehlay hi jald fatah karade
  48,28,wohi to hai jis ne apne paighambar ko hadaayat ( ki kitaab ) aur deen haq day kar bheja taakay is ko tamam deeno par ghalib kere. aur haq zahir karne ke liye khuda hi kaafi hai
  48,29,"Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam khuda ke paighambar hain aur jo log un ke sath hain woh kafiroon ke haq mein sakht hain aur aapas mein reham dil, ( ae dekhnay walay ) to un ko daikhta hai ke ( khuda ke agay ) jhuke hue sir bsjod hain aur khuda ka fazl aur is ki khushnodi talab kar rahay hain. ( kasrate ) sajiood ke assar se un ki pishanyon par nishaan parre hue hain. un ke yahi Awsaf torat mein ( marqoom ) hain. aur yahi Awsaf injeel mein hain. ( woh ) goya aik khaiti hain jis ne ( pehlay zameen se ) apni soi nikaali phir is ko mazbootkiya phir mouti hui aur phir apni naal par seedhi khari hogayi aur lagi khaiti walon ko khush karne taakay kafiroon ka jee jalaaye. jo log un mein se imaan laaye aur naik amal karte rahay un se khuda ne gunaaho ki bakhshish aur ajar azeem ka wadakiya hai"
